  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Compare clinical outcomes of endoscopic pilonidal sinus treatment (EPSiT) with excision
      treatment with a randomised clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Primary outcome: complication rate Secondary outcomes: Quality of life, recurrence rate,
      length of stay, post operative pain (NRS), return to work time, time to complete wound
      healing, resource use.

      Allocation ratio 2:1
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
